OL,7,FThe Welsh Conservatives have resigned
OL,8,Ffrom a cross-party Senedd committee
OL,9,Flooking at how Wales responded to the
OL,10,FCovid pandemic after Labour rejected a
OL,11,Fmotion which would have allowed
OL,12,Fwitnesses, including ministers, to
OL,13,Fgive evidence under oath.
