OL,7,FThe Wales Covid-19 Inquiry Special
OL,8,FPurpose Committee was set up by the
OL,9,FSenedd to look at reports at each
OL,10,Fstage of the UK Covid-19 Inquiry and
OL,11,Fpropose to the Senedd by motion, any
OL,12,Fgaps identified in the preparedness
OL,13,Fand response of the Welsh Government
OL,14,Fand other Welsh public bodies during
OL,15,Fthe pandemic that should be subject to
OL,16,Ffurther examination.
OL,18,FTwo of the committee's six members
OL,19,Fwere occupied by Welsh Conservative
OL,20,FMSs, Tom Giffard and Sam Rowlands.
