OL,7,FTom Giffard MS, who co-chaired the
OL,8,Fcommittee, said: "It is with a heavy
OL,9,Fheart that I have resigned as co-chair
OL,10,Fof the Senedd's Wales-Covid 19 Inquiry
OL,11,FSpecial Purpose Committee, and that
OL,12,Fthe Welsh Conservatives will no longer
OL,13,Fengage with the committee.
OL,15,F"The Covid-19 pandemic devastated
OL,16,Flives, and its consequences are still
OL,17,Fbeing felt. Families who lost loved
OL,18,Fones deserve honest answers, yet
OL,19,FLabour's decision to block oaths being
OL,20,Ftaken undermines any chance of getting
OL,21,Fto the truth.
