OL,7,F"We entered into this committee in
OL,8,Fgood faith, hoping that the Welsh
OL,9,FLabour Government would be a good
OL,10,Ffaith partner. Unfortunately, almost
OL,11,Fevery suggestion of greater scrutiny
OL,12,Fof those decisions is met with fierce
OL,13,Fresistance by either the Welsh Labour
OL,14,FGovernment ` or often, the Labour
OL,15,Fmembers that sit on it.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
