OL,3,CTories quit Senedd Covid committee
OL,4,Cafter Labour reject ministers taking
OL,5,Coath
OL,7,F"Without the safeguard of requiring
OL,8,Fwitnesses to speak under oath, this
OL,9,Fcommittee has become a pointless
OL,10,Ftalking shop. I refuse to be part of a
OL,11,Fprocess that fails to give the public
OL,12,Fthe answers they deserve.
OL,14,F"The Welsh Conservatives have now
OL,15,Fwithdrawn from the committee and will
OL,16,Fcontinue to call for a full Wales-wide
OL,17,Finquiry into the Covid-19 pandemic."
