OL,7,FShe told the Senedd: "Using a
OL,8,Fdiscretionary power to introduce an
OL,9,Foath would hinder, we believe, the
OL,10,Ffree flow of information between
OL,11,Fpeople giving evidence and the Special
OL,12,FPurposes committee. Those invited may
OL,13,Fbecome more reluctant to attend, feel
OL,14,Fcompelled to take legal advice before
OL,15,Fattending or indeed curtail their
OL,16,Fanswers to fact only. And we can't see
OL,17,Fwhere the benefits which have been
OL,18,Farticulated by others today can
OL,19,Foutweigh the significant risk and
OL,20,Fimpact of this result.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/9
