OL,3,CTories quit Senedd Covid committee
OL,4,Cafter Labour reject ministers taking
OL,5,Coath
OL,7,F"There is already a judge-led inquiry
OL,8,Finto the Covid-19 pandemic that is
OL,9,Fconstituted and resourced to operate
OL,10,Fin this way, and we must allow that
OL,11,Finquiry to continue to do its
OL,12,Fimportant work.
OL,14,F"We will continue to support that
OL,15,Finquiry to ensure we learn the lessons
OL,16,Fin memory of those who lost their
OL,17,Flives during the pandemic.
