OL,3,CTories quit Senedd Covid committee
OL,4,Cafter Labour reject ministers taking
OL,5,Coath
OL,7,F"We have a proud history of
OL,8,Ftransparency and openness. In this
OL,9,Fsense, we won't be supporting this
OL,10,Fmotion, which we believe would seek to
OL,11,Fundermine these values, but we do
OL,12,Fvalue the work of the Special Purpose
OL,13,Fcross-party, which is a cross-party
OL,14,Fcommittee. We thank the members for
OL,15,Ftheir important work and we look
OL,16,Fforward to the debate next week on
OL,17,Ftheir first report."
